cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on automatic image annotation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed model uses recurrent neural networks, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the model using top-k retrieval performance, which is a common measure in information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper evaluates the model on various image annotation datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
